{
 "name": "RPlog_Snowball_Fight",
 "title": "Snowball Fight",
 "summary": "On a snowy night in Fountain Square, the drunk and depressed Ambassador Morganna Tazecks stumbles in and kicks a news terminal, drawing the attention of the equally inebriated Troy and the disapproving Rodo. When Troy's errant snowball clips the cloaked ambassador, an all-out brawl erupts: Morganna tackles and flips Troy into a snowbank while the businessman Hugo Dracolysk, Troy's sister Stelita, and the watchful aide Kaley pile into the chaos of flying snow, slips, and shoves. Kaley drags the tipsy Morganna behind a tree to chastise her conduct and ask after Ozzle, while Troy, Dracolysk, and Stelita keep tumbling around the fountain. Eventually the bruised, snow-caked diplomat dusts herself off, repays Kaley with a snowball down the back, and fumbles off to sleep away the alcohol.",
